# Principal Component Analysis (PCA)

This folder contains Jupyter notebooks implementing Principal Component Analysis (PCA) for dimensionality reduction on the UNSW-NB15 dataset.

## Files

- UNSW-PCA-10.ipynb – PCA with 10 principal components
- UNSW-PCA-20.ipynb – PCA with 20 principal components
- UNSW-PCA-30.ipynb – PCA with 30 principal components

## Objective

Compare different PCA configurations and analyze their effect on intrusion detection performance.
